e_Buck\", \"score\": 0.9418516842940009, \"rank\": 0.0446646026810258, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Buck\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Buck\"}, {\"begin\": 6346, \"end\": 6353, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_O'Neill\", \"score\": 0.994489195407006, \"rank\": 0.0046665081755259755, \"text\": \"O'Neill\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_O'Neill\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_O'Neill\"}, {\"begin\": 6525, \"end\": 6528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.95448574307401, \"rank\": 0.04768458539736475, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is no proof to support these claims from a reputable organisation and the coverage has been very selective.\", \"from\": 6564, \"to\": 6678, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's too early to say anything without any actual proof,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 6679, \"to\": 6745, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Irish Amateur Boxing Association (IABA), which governs the sport in Ireland, is a member of the IBA.\", \"from\": 6747, \"to\": 6851, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6751, \"end\": 6783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Athletic_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Irish Amateur Boxing Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Athletic_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Athletic_Boxing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 6785, \"end\": 6789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Athletic_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, 